    "description": "Taj Hotels Retail Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Visual Merchandiser at our Patna location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Taj Hotels Retail Holdings Services:\nTaj Hotels Retail Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Build relationships with regular customers to drive loyalty\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Category Management\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n• Proficiency in Retail Analytics\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Customer Service\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Taj Hotels Retail Holdings Services!",
